{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"0ac43db3c8","title":"毛泽东关于陶铸问题的讲话","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"5a5acf2955","index":0,"year":1967,"month":1,"day":8,"articleId":"0ac43db3c8"}],"tags":[{"id":"4206ce6bf3","name":"红卫兵运动","type":"主题/事件"},{"id":"5bd9678625","name":"邓小平","type":"人物"},{"id":"dbcf15bd08","name":"陶铸","type":"人物"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"},{"id":"e23dcf99fa","name":"发言","type":"文稿类型"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"GPCRv3","name":"中国文化大革命文库（第三版）","internal":true,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"GPCRv3":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"f14755b816","type":"title","text":"关于陶铸问题的讲话","index":0,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"0ac43db3c8"},{"id":"50b8261312","type":"authors","text":"毛泽东","index":1,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"0ac43db3c8"},{"id":"d82a265597","type":"paragraph","text":"陶铸问题很严重。陶铸是邓小平介绍到中央来的。这个人极不老实，邓小平说还可以。陶铸在十一中全会以前坚决执行了刘邓路线，十一中全会后也执行了刘邓路线。在红卫兵接见时，在报纸上和电视里照片有刘邓镜头，是陶铸安排的。陶铸领导下的几个部都垮了。那些部可以不要，搞革命不一定非要部。教育部管不了，文化部管不了，我们也管不了，红卫兵一来就管住了。","index":2,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"0ac43db3c8"},{"id":"b637c844c7","type":"paragraph","text":"陶铸的问题我们没有解决了，红卫兵起来就解决了。","index":3,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"0ac43db3c8"}],"page":{"id":"ebf6807a5d","publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"0ac43db3c8","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}